-----

## Table of Contents

- [Installation](#installation)
- [License](#license)

## Installation

```console
pip install dander
```

## Usage

### `json` Utilities

#### Split a JSON file into multiple files

```bash
dander json split file.json
```

#### Format a JSON file with indents

```bash
dander json format file.json --write
```

